org.gvsig.jts.voronoi.chew
Class DTriangulationForJTS

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.jts.voronoi.chew.DTriangulationForJTS

public class DTriangulationForJTS
extends java.lang.Object

OpenJUMP's modified version by gvSIG project. We have exchange List for VoronoiAndTinInputLyr, and passed CancellableProgressTask as parameter of those methods we want to monitor its progress. The TIN's implemented algorithm is incremental delaunay triangulation, which starts with a triangle that contains all mess points, and subdivides it with each new inserted vertex.

Author:
sstein, azabala(adapter to gvsig) Use the class to access the delauney trinagulation by L. Paul Chew Methods of the class are modified versions from DelaunayPanel.java in DelaunayAp.java.
